"To define the positions enter the :menuselection:`Accounting module --> "
"Configuration --> Budgetary Positions`."
msgstr ""
"Om de posities in te geven gaat u naar  :menuselection:`Boekhouding --> "
"Configuratie --> Budgetaire posities`."

